The performance of the GQDs were analysed by using the Stern-Volmer equation. The KSV values obtained from the slope (Table 1
                        ) of Fig. 6
                        , correlation coefficient values(R2),percent relative standard deviation (%RSD) values (for five determinations) as well as the detection limit of analytes (Table 2
                        ) indicated that GQDs were effective for sensing of nitrophenols.
